This is a bot for the vendecookies game. You can find more info in its website:

    http://www.vendecookies.com

If you don't have any referal and you want to help you, you can introduce my
nickname (pokoli) as referal, so I will get some help with your efforts.


Requirements
============

This program requires the requests python library in order to work, so you can
install it by running:

    pip install requests

or

    pip install -r requirements.txt



Configuration
=============

In order to configure your username and password you must edit the config.py
file and enter your vendecookies credentials there.


Usage
=====

Just run the script with:

    python vendecookies.py

The script will end when it founds a game that can not be solved automatically
(or currently don't know how to solve it).
